snippet.title: Plain Opening - Yuri Jam 2016
snippet.description:
Riley is a completely unremarkable woman, if you were to ask her.
A plane ride towards a job that could change her destiny ends in disaster when there's a critical engine failure during flight. It would be the end for Riley too, were it not for a remarkable woman who claims to be from the year 2165.

A Yuri Jam 2016 game by Fablesoft Studios and co.

Check out the game here: https://lemmasoft.renai.us/forums/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=40550
